name: Experiment Or Die #119
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. A handful of the designs in this collection deal with the idea of exploration. It is human nature to seek out places that man has never been to whether it be undiscovered lands, the ocean, or outer space. Continuing to push the limits of what we know as a species has and always will be an integral factor in our development and evolution. If you no longer yearn for knowledge then you might as well throw in the towel. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk.
